title: 668. Ohio State head coach Ryan Day on QB Justin Fields
itunes:title: 668. Ohio State head coach Ryan Day on QB Justin Fields
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks! In this special edition, DJ and Bucky are joined by Ohio State head football coach Ryan Day to discuss the growth of quarterback Justin Fields, who became a top NFL prospect during his playing years at OSU. Day speaks about the process of Fields transferring from Georgia, his growth with the program, and what he will bring to an NFL team as a top ten draft prospect. Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
